name: MyButler
0:
”Alexa, ask my butler whose turn it is to do the dishes out of family”
”Alexa, ask my butler whose turn it is to take out the trash out of everybody”
”Alexa, ask my butler who lives here”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my butler
des: This skill lets you avoid household negotiations about whose turn it is to do daily chores. Instead, just ask the butler, and the butler will randomly assign someone from the household to manage the task!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
